---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Prodigious
description: Playground of half-baked ideas.
date: 2000-01-01
---
<main id="main" class="container flow">
    <h1 class="home-heading">Prodigious <span class="home-subheading">(adj.)</span></h1>
    <p class="callout">: causing amazement or wonder</p>

    <h2>check out these things:</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><a href="/blog/">blog</a> - regular blog stuff</li>
        <li><a href="/notes/">notes</a> - thoughts not long enough for a blog post</li>
        <li><a href="/commonplace/">commonplace book</a> - collection of things that interest me</li>
        <li><a href="https://photos.tedmehl.me">photos</a> - I sometimes take photos, and I sometimes post them</li>
        <li><a href="/demos/">demos</a> - ideas I bothered to make real</li>
    </ul>

    <details>
        <summary>why prodigious?</summary>
        <div class="details-wrapper flow">
            <p>One of my favorite movies is October Sky. Quentin, a main character, often says "Prodigious!" when
                something amazing happens and for some reason that has stuck with me.</p>

            <p>If you haven't watched the movie before, you should. It's a look into a small coal town in West Virginia
                and a group of friends dreaming about things beyond it. Based on the memoir of NASA engineer Homer
                Hickam.</p>
        </div>
    </details>

    {# Future section where I link to my most recent post and note #}

    <h2>read the latest</h2>
    {% set posts = collections.posts | reverse %}
    {% set latestPost = posts[0] %}
    {% set notes = collections.notes | reverse %}
    {% set latestNote = notes[0] %}
    <div class="feature-grid">
    <div class="feature-grid-feature">
        <div class="feature-body">
            <h3 class="feature-title">{{ latestPost.data.title }}</h3>
            <div class="feature-content">
                <p>{{ latestPost.data.description }}</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-footer"><span class="feature-type">blog post</span><p><a href="{{latestPost.url}}">read the post &rarr;</a></p></div>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-grid-feature">
        <div class="feature-body">
            <h3 class="feature-title">{{ latestNote.data.title}}</h3>
            <div class="feature-content">
                <p>{{ latestNote.data.description }}</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-footer"><span class="feature-type">note</span><p><a href="{{latestNote.url}}">read the note &rarr;</a></p></div>

    </div>
    </div>
    
</main>